Time":"2020-05-28T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"//第228章 《簡易程序治罪條例》<br />\n4. 在公眾地方犯的妨擾罪等<br />\n<br />\n任何人無合法權限或解釋而 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(1) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>將任何</strong></span>腐肉、污垢、泥土、稻草、糞便，或其他髒物、廢料、<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>發出惡臭或令人厭惡的物品拋擲或放置在任何公眾地方、政府財產</strong></span>(獲公職人員同意者除外)或私人財產(獲該私人財產的擁有人及佔用人(如有)的同意者除外)上；<br />\n<br />\n可處罰款$500或監禁3個月。//<br />\n<br />\n唔駛諗肯定又係「公眾妨擾罪」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172ac0d906763114ab2cf3b0ff09c32d4be80153","tid":2039322,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9a11bc26aee9f554be8c997fde5192942abab6","tid":2039322,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4548912cc494a252faef8dfafb29af0bb572a73c","tid":2039322,"uid":127176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178983dfec1e3c10e1df37785055f163b47c5533","tid":2039322,"uid":208011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"早兩日 郭卓堅申請司法覆被拒<br />\n法庭：一般不干預立法會的內部事務<br />\n轉個頭<br />\n法庭：議員掉爛草違法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553f7437fea44474bb2ff9850721d103aba34de0","tid":2039322,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"大家都進化了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fac5f6988ff1115f4750f78